title: NFL ATL: DeSean landing spots, winners and losers
itunes:title: NFL ATL: DeSean landing spots, winners and losers
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra -- breaks down the latest turn in the offseason saga of DeSean Jackson and puts some sandwiches on the line with regards to where they think the recently released receiver will land.  Elsewhere, the gang sifts through the frenzied reactions to Johnny Manziel’s pro day performance and goes over this week’s biggest winners and losers.
